'''Maṛtina Hingis''' d tanaddalt n Tennis Taswisit ilulen ass n 30 Ctuber 1980 di Košice (tamurt n Sluvaki, zikenni čekusluvaki). D nettat id tanaddalt meẓẓilen ig bḍen ad teḥrez talɣuɣa n Grand Chhelem si zman n Lottie Dod asegwas 1887, d nettat daɣen id tanaddalt tameẓlant ig bḍen ɣer tqacuct n wedras umaḍan deg umezruy n Tennis.

Tettmeslay Kuz (4) n tutlayin, Tačikit, Talmanit (taswist talmanit), tagyizit d tefṛansist.
Tella t tteffaɣ d unaddal Serǧiu Garsia, sin akkin tessen amyurar n Tennis Radek Stepanek asegwas n 2006. Tezweǧ ak-d umennay afṛansi Tibau Hutin asegwas n 2010.

==Temẓ-is==

Tluled s yisem Martina Hingisová di tmurt n Sluvaki zikenni čekusluvaki, seg mi tesεa 8 isegwasen Maṛtina tettidir di tmurt Taswist acku yemmas tεiwed zwaǧ. Deg usegwas n 1999 tuγ axxam deg temdint n Floride [[Marikan]] maca teqqim tettidir di teswist, d yemmas is yefkan isem n Maṛtina, imi tella tḥemmel tanadalt tameqṛant n Tennis Maṛtina Navṛatiluva, nettat daγen n tmurt n čekusluvaki. Yemmas tella tetturar addal n Tennis, dγa d ayen itt yeǧǧan attili d tasleγmayt n Maṛtina deg umecwaṛ ines maṛṛa.

==Amecwaṛ ines seg (1994-2002)==

Maṛtina telmed att urar addal n Tennis si temẓ-is, γurs 5 isegwasen di lεemr-is mi tebda tetturar di tedwilin, tessaweḍ att uγal d talγuγt n umaḍal n tullas asegwas n 1994. asegwas n 1996 turar aked Helena Suková deg uslig n Wimledon, dγa tuγal d tanadalt tameẓlant yessawḍen at ḥrez talγuγa agi.

Asegwas n 1997 d win ig walan urar n maṛtina ad yuγal qessaḥ nezzah, tarbaḥ 37 raren wa deffir wayeḍ, d 6 telγuγa, tebwi Open n lustṛali mgal Mary pierce 6-2 6-2, tebweḍ γer tagara n Rolland Garros anda texṣer d Iva Majoli acku tuḍen cwiṭ di tagara, tebwi daγen Wimbledon mgal Novotna aked US Open d Venus Williams 6-4 6-0; d ayen itt yeǧǧan att awi Clem amecṭuḥ.

Tebwi kṛad n talγiwin n Grand Chelem yemgaraden, ala Rolland Garros it xṣen sin ibardan di tagara, asegwas n 1999 anda turar aked tanadalt tameqṛant [[Steffi Graf]] ig llan di tagara n'umecwaṛ ines deg addal n Tennis, teqqimed deg umezruy, acku Maṛtina tεac asenni yiwen wass ur tezmir attettu, tella tarbaḥ urar deg aḥric amezwaru, sinna yellad umgarad garas d unefray, ayen yeǧǧan ula d-imfarǧen (imeshanayen) ad ddun d [[Steffi Graf]], di tagara, Maṛtina texṣer talγuγa, teffeγ seg urar s-imeṭṭawen, ayen werǧin n wala deg addal agi.
Seg ass nni Maṛtina ut tebwi talγuγa n Grand chelem, teqqim deg umḍiq amezwaru deg ubellez umaḍal, acku trbbaḥ aṭas n telγuγa it tturar, maca ur tebwi ara talγuγa tameqṛant.

asegwas n 2002 texṣer daγen di tagara n Open n lustṛali mgal Jennifer Kapriati, deg urar daγen id yeqqimen deg umezruy aladγa Maṛtina tella teḥrez aḥric amezwaru 6-4, yarna deg wis-sin tella tezwar 4-0, sinna 5-1, ar-mi dezzi fellas Jennifer, tifesniwin di temdint n Melbourne bḍen-t γer 50°c, ayen yeǧǧan Maṛtina att xṣer zdat Jennifer.
